On the topic of glbt;

So apparently gay marriage is all but assured at this point in the usa.  Why?  Cause the opposition *REALLY* fucked up during the legal briefing.  To use an analogy imagine two runners in the 100 meter sprint; instead one of the two when they hear the starting pistol go off they go "nosedive" and jumps headfirst into sprint track acting as though they're about to swim.

How did they fuck up so bad?  They presented next to no legal reasoning as to why it should remain banned.
